name: Lower Level Queen
description: Nestled in Vasastan, Clas på hörnet Hotel revitalizes an 18th-century tavern into a sophisticated boutique, preserving original details and craftsmanship. The apartment is located quite centrally in Stockholm, about a 15-20 minute walk from the city center, and a 1-2 minute walk to the nearest subway station (Stadion). The apartment has a bathroom, a small kitchen with a sink, mini fridge with a small section for frozen stuff, and a stove.
